{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Everybody in our society's life is touched by cancer --"},{"time":3000,"text":"if not personally,"},{"time":5000,"text":"then through a loved one, a family member,"},{"time":8000,"text":"colleague, friend."},{"time":10000,"text":"And once our lives are touched by cancer,"},{"time":13000,"text":"we quickly learn"},{"time":15000,"text":"that there are basically"},{"time":17000,"text":"three weapons, or three tools, that are available"},{"time":20000,"text":"to fight the disease:"},{"time":23000,"text":"surgery, radiation and chemotherapy."},{"time":26000,"text":"And once we get involved"},{"time":29000,"text":"in the therapeutic decisions,"},{"time":32000,"text":"again either personally"},{"time":34000,"text":"or with our loved ones and family members,"},{"time":37000,"text":"we also very quickly learn"},{"time":40000,"text":"the benefits, the trade-offs and the limitations"},{"time":43000,"text":"of these tools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45000,"text":"I'm very thankful to Jay and to Mark"},{"time":47000,"text":"and the TEDMED team"},{"time":49000,"text":"for inviting me today"},{"time":51000,"text":"to describe a fourth tool, a new tool,"},{"time":54000,"text":"that we call Tumor Treating Fields."},{"time":57000,"text":"Tumor Treating Fields"},{"time":59000,"text":"were invented by Dr. Yoram Palti,"},{"time":62000,"text":"professor emeritus at the Technion in Israel."},{"time":65000,"text":"And they use low-intensity"},{"time":67000,"text":"electric fields"},{"time":69000,"text":"to fight cancer."},{"time":71000,"text":"To understand how Tumor Treating Fields work,"},{"time":74000,"text":"we first need to understand"},{"time":76000,"text":"what are electric fields."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"Let me first address"},{"time":81000,"text":"a few popular misconceptions."},{"time":84000,"text":"First of all, electric fields"},{"time":86000,"text":"are not an electric current"},{"time":88000,"text":"that is coursing through the tissue."},{"time":91000,"text":"Electric fields"},{"time":93000,"text":"are not ionizing radiation,"},{"time":95000,"text":"like X-rays or proton beams,"},{"time":97000,"text":"that bombard tissue"},{"time":99000,"text":"to disrupt DNA."},{"time":101000,"text":"And electric fields"},{"time":103000,"text":"are not magnetism."},{"time":105000,"text":"What electric fields are"},{"time":107000,"text":"are a field of forces."},{"time":110000,"text":"And these forces"},{"time":112000,"text":"act on, attract, bodies"},{"time":115000,"text":"that have an electrical charge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"The best way to visualize an electric field"},{"time":120000,"text":"is to think of gravity."},{"time":122000,"text":"Gravity is also a field of forces"},{"time":125000,"text":"that act on masses."},{"time":127000,"text":"We can all picture astronauts in space."},{"time":130000,"text":"They float freely in three dimensions"},{"time":132000,"text":"without any forces acting on them."},{"time":134000,"text":"But as that space shuttle"},{"time":137000,"text":"returns to Earth,"},{"time":139000,"text":"and as the astronauts enter the Earth's gravitational field,"},{"time":142000,"text":"they begin to see the effects of gravity."},{"time":145000,"text":"They begin to be attracted towards Earth."},{"time":147000,"text":"And as they land,"},{"time":149000,"text":"they're fully aligned in the gravitational field."},{"time":151000,"text":"We're, of course, all stuck in the Earth's gravitational field right now."},{"time":154000,"text":"That's why you're all in your chairs."},{"time":157000,"text":"And that's why we have to use our muscle energy"},{"time":159000,"text":"to stand up, to walk around"},{"time":161000,"text":"and to lift things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"In cancer,"},{"time":166000,"text":"cells rapidly divide"},{"time":168000,"text":"and lead to uncontrolled tumor growth."},{"time":171000,"text":"We can think of a cell"},{"time":174000,"text":"from an electrical perspective"},{"time":176000,"text":"as if it's a mini space station."},{"time":179000,"text":"And in that space station"},{"time":181000,"text":"we have the genetic material, the chromosomes,"},{"time":184000,"text":"within a nucleus."},{"time":186000,"text":"And out in the cytoplasmic soup"},{"time":188000,"text":"we have special proteins"},{"time":190000,"text":"that are required for cell division"},{"time":192000,"text":"that float freely in this soup"},{"time":194000,"text":"in three dimensions."},{"time":196000,"text":"Importantly, those special proteins"},{"time":199000,"text":"are among the most highly charged objects"},{"time":202000,"text":"in our body."},{"time":204000,"text":"As cell division begins"},{"time":206000,"text":"the nucleus disintegrates,"},{"time":208000,"text":"the chromosomes line up"},{"time":210000,"text":"in the middle of the cell"},{"time":212000,"text":"and those special proteins"},{"time":214000,"text":"undergo a three-dimensional sequence"},{"time":218000,"text":"whereby they attach"},{"time":220000,"text":"and they literally click into place end-on-end"},{"time":223000,"text":"to form chains."},{"time":225000,"text":"These chains"},{"time":227000,"text":"then progress and attach"},{"time":229000,"text":"to the genetic material"},{"time":232000,"text":"and pull the genetic material"},{"time":234000,"text":"from one cell into two cells."},{"time":236000,"text":"And this is exactly how"},{"time":238000,"text":"one cancer cell becomes two cancer cells,"},{"time":240000,"text":"two cancer cells become four cancer cells,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and we have ultimately"},{"time":244000,"text":"uncontrolled tumor growth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247000,"text":"Tumor Treating Fields"},{"time":250000,"text":"use externally placed transducers"},{"time":254000,"text":"attached to a field generator"},{"time":257000,"text":"to create an artificial electric field"},{"time":261000,"text":"on that space station."},{"time":264000,"text":"And when that cellular space station"},{"time":267000,"text":"is within the electric field,"},{"time":269000,"text":"it acts on those highly charged proteins"},{"time":273000,"text":"and aligns them."},{"time":275000,"text":"And it prevents them from forming those chains,"},{"time":278000,"text":"those mitotic spindles,"},{"time":280000,"text":"that are necessary to pull the genetic material"},{"time":283000,"text":"into the daughter cells."},{"time":285000,"text":"What we see is that the cells will attempt to divide"},{"time":288000,"text":"for several hours."},{"time":290000,"text":"And they will either enter into"},{"time":293000,"text":"this so-called cellular suicide,"},{"time":295000,"text":"programmed cell death,"},{"time":297000,"text":"or they will form unhealthy daughter cells"},{"time":300000,"text":"and enter into apoptosis"},{"time":303000,"text":"once they have divided."},{"time":305000,"text":"And we can observe this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"What I'm going to show you next"},{"time":309000,"text":"are two in vitro experiments."},{"time":311000,"text":"This is cultures, identical cultures,"},{"time":314000,"text":"of cervical cancer cells."},{"time":316000,"text":"And we've stained these cultures"},{"time":318000,"text":"with a green florescent dye"},{"time":320000,"text":"so that we can look at these proteins"},{"time":323000,"text":"that form these chains."},{"time":325000,"text":"The first clip shows"},{"time":327000,"text":"a normal cell division"},{"time":330000,"text":"without the Tumor Treating Fields."},{"time":333000,"text":"What we see"},{"time":335000,"text":"are, first of all, a very active culture,"},{"time":337000,"text":"a lot of divisions,"},{"time":339000,"text":"and then very clear nuclei"},{"time":341000,"text":"once the cells have separated."},{"time":343000,"text":"And we can see them dividing throughout."},{"time":345000,"text":"When we apply the fields --"},{"time":347000,"text":"again, in the identical time-scale"},{"time":349000,"text":"to the identical culture --"},{"time":351000,"text":"you're going to see something different."},{"time":353000,"text":"The cells round up for division,"},{"time":355000,"text":"but they're very static in that position."},{"time":358000,"text":"We'll see two cells"},{"time":360000,"text":"in the upper part of the screen"},{"time":365000,"text":"attempting to divide."},{"time":367000,"text":"The one within the circle manages."},{"time":369000,"text":"But see how much of the protein"},{"time":371000,"text":"is still throughout the nucleus,"},{"time":373000,"text":"even in the dividing cell."},{"time":375000,"text":"The one up there can't divide at all."},{"time":377000,"text":"And then this bubbling, this membrane bubbling,"},{"time":380000,"text":"is the hallmark"},{"time":382000,"text":"of apoptosis in this cell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385000,"text":"Formation of healthy mitotic spindles"},{"time":389000,"text":"is necessary for division"},{"time":392000,"text":"in all cell types."},{"time":394000,"text":"We've applied Tumor Treating Fields"},{"time":396000,"text":"to over 20 different cancers in the lab,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and we see this effect"},{"time":401000,"text":"in all of them."},{"time":404000,"text":"Now importantly,"},{"time":406000,"text":"these Tumor Treating Fields have no effect"},{"time":409000,"text":"on normal undividing cells."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"10 years ago,"},{"time":413000,"text":"Dr. Palti founded a company called Novocure"},{"time":416000,"text":"to develop his discovery"},{"time":419000,"text":"into a practical therapy for patients."},{"time":422000,"text":"In that time, Novocure's developed two systems --"},{"time":426000,"text":"one system for cancers in the head"},{"time":429000,"text":"and another system for cancers in the trunk of the body."},{"time":432000,"text":"The first cancer that we have focused on"},{"time":435000,"text":"is the deadly brain cancer, GBM."},{"time":438000,"text":"GBM affects about 10,000 people"},{"time":441000,"text":"in the U.S. each year."},{"time":444000,"text":"It's a death sentence."},{"time":446000,"text":"The expected five year survival"},{"time":448000,"text":"is less than five percent."},{"time":450000,"text":"And the typical patient"},{"time":452000,"text":"with optimal therapy"},{"time":454000,"text":"survives just a little over a year,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and only about seven months"},{"time":459000,"text":"from the time that the cancer is first treated"},{"time":462000,"text":"and then comes back and starts growing again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467000,"text":"Novocure conducted"},{"time":469000,"text":"its first phase three randomized trial"},{"time":471000,"text":"in patients with recurrent GBM."},{"time":473000,"text":"So these are patients"},{"time":475000,"text":"who had received surgery,"},{"time":479000,"text":"high dose radiation to the head"},{"time":481000,"text":"and first-line chemotherapy,"},{"time":483000,"text":"and that had failed and their tumors had grown back."},{"time":486000,"text":"We divided the patients into two groups."},{"time":489000,"text":"The first group received second-line chemotherapy,"},{"time":492000,"text":"which is expected to double the life expectancy,"},{"time":495000,"text":"versus no treatment at all."},{"time":497000,"text":"And then the second group"},{"time":499000,"text":"received only Tumor Treating Field therapy."},{"time":502000,"text":"What we saw in that trial"},{"time":504000,"text":"is that that the life expectancies of both groups --"},{"time":507000,"text":"so the chemotherapy treated group"},{"time":509000,"text":"and the Tumor Treating Field group --"},{"time":511000,"text":"was the same."},{"time":513000,"text":"But importantly,"},{"time":515000,"text":"the Tumor Treating Field group"},{"time":518000,"text":"suffered none of the side effects"},{"time":521000,"text":"typical of chemotherapy patients."},{"time":524000,"text":"They had no pain,"},{"time":526000,"text":"suffered none of the infections."},{"time":529000,"text":"They had no nausea, diarrhea,"},{"time":532000,"text":"constipation, fatigue"},{"time":535000,"text":"that would be expected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"Based on this trial,"},{"time":539000,"text":"in April of this year,"},{"time":541000,"text":"the FDA approved Tumor Treating Fields"},{"time":544000,"text":"for the treatment of patients"},{"time":546000,"text":"with recurrent GBM."},{"time":549000,"text":"Importantly, it was the first time ever"},{"time":552000,"text":"that the FDA included"},{"time":554000,"text":"in their approval of an oncology treatment"},{"time":557000,"text":"a quality of life claim."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561000,"text":"So I'm going to show you now"},{"time":564000,"text":"one of the patients"},{"time":566000,"text":"from this trial."},{"time":569000,"text":"Robert Dill-Bundi"},{"time":571000,"text":"is a famous Swiss cycling champion."},{"time":573000,"text":"He won the gold medal in Moscow"},{"time":575000,"text":"in the 4,000 meter pursuit."},{"time":578000,"text":"And five years ago,"},{"time":581000,"text":"Robert was diagnosed with GBM."},{"time":584000,"text":"He received the standard treatments."},{"time":586000,"text":"He received surgery."},{"time":589000,"text":"He received high dose radiation to the head."},{"time":592000,"text":"And he received first-line chemotherapy."},{"time":595000,"text":"A year after this treatment --"},{"time":597000,"text":"in fact, this is his baseline MRI."},{"time":600000,"text":"You can see that the black regions"},{"time":603000,"text":"in the upper right quadrant"},{"time":605000,"text":"are the areas where he had surgery."},{"time":607000,"text":"And a year after that treatment,"},{"time":609000,"text":"his tumor grew back with a vengeance."},{"time":612000,"text":"That cloudy white mass that you see"},{"time":615000,"text":"is the recurrence of the tumor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618000,"text":"At this point, he was told by his doctors"},{"time":621000,"text":"that he had about 3 months to live."},{"time":624000,"text":"He entered our trial."},{"time":626000,"text":"And here we can see him getting the therapy."},{"time":629000,"text":"First of all, these electrodes are noninvasive."},{"time":632000,"text":"They're attached to the skin"},{"time":634000,"text":"in the area of the tumor."},{"time":636000,"text":"Here you can see"},{"time":638000,"text":"that a technician is placing them on there much like bandages."},{"time":641000,"text":"The patients learn to do this themselves"},{"time":644000,"text":"And then the patients"},{"time":647000,"text":"can undergo all the activities of their daily life."},{"time":650000,"text":"There's none of the tiredness."},{"time":652000,"text":"There's none of what is called the \"chemo head.\""},{"time":655000,"text":"There's no sensation."},{"time":657000,"text":"It doesn't interfere"},{"time":659000,"text":"with computers or electrical equipment."},{"time":662000,"text":"And the therapy is delivered continuously"},{"time":664000,"text":"at home,"},{"time":666000,"text":"without having to go into the hospital"},{"time":668000,"text":"either periodically or continually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671000,"text":"These are Robert's MRIs,"},{"time":674000,"text":"again, under only TTField treatment."},{"time":677000,"text":"This is a therapy that takes time to work."},{"time":680000,"text":"It's a medical device;"},{"time":682000,"text":"it works when it's on."},{"time":684000,"text":"But what we can see is, by month six,"},{"time":686000,"text":"the tumor has responded"},{"time":689000,"text":"and it's begun to melt away."},{"time":692000,"text":"It's still there."},{"time":694000,"text":"By month 12,"},{"time":696000,"text":"we could argue whether"},{"time":698000,"text":"there's a little bit of material around the edges,"},{"time":700000,"text":"but it's essentially completely gone."},{"time":703000,"text":"It's now five years"},{"time":705000,"text":"since Robert's diagnosis,"},{"time":707000,"text":"and he's alive,"},{"time":710000,"text":"but importantly, he's healthy"},{"time":712000,"text":"and he's at work."},{"time":714000,"text":"I'm going to let him, in this very short clip,"},{"time":716000,"text":"describe his impressions of the therapy"},{"time":718000,"text":"in his own words."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720000,"text":"(Video) Robert Dill-Bundi: My quality of life,"},{"time":722000,"text":"I rate what I have today"},{"time":724000,"text":"a bit different than what most people would assume."},{"time":728000,"text":"I am the happiest, the happiest person in the world."},{"time":733000,"text":"And every single morning I appreciate life."},{"time":737000,"text":"Every night I fall asleep very well,"},{"time":740000,"text":"and I am, I repeat,"},{"time":743000,"text":"the happiest man in the world,"},{"time":745000,"text":"and I'm thankful I am alive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":750000,"text":"BD: Novocure's also working on lung cancer"},{"time":753000,"text":"as the second target."},{"time":755000,"text":"We've run a phase two trial"},{"time":757000,"text":"in Switzerland"},{"time":759000,"text":"on, again, recurrent patients --"},{"time":761000,"text":"patients who have received standard therapy"},{"time":764000,"text":"and whose cancer has come back."},{"time":767000,"text":"I'm going to show you another clip"},{"time":769000,"text":"of a woman named Lydia."},{"time":771000,"text":"Lydia's a 66 year-old farmer"},{"time":773000,"text":"in Switzerland."},{"time":775000,"text":"She was diagnosed with lung cancer"},{"time":777000,"text":"five years ago."},{"time":779000,"text":"She underwent four different regimes of chemotherapy"},{"time":782000,"text":"over two years,"},{"time":784000,"text":"none of which had an effect."},{"time":786000,"text":"Her cancer continued to grow."},{"time":788000,"text":"Three years ago,"},{"time":790000,"text":"she entered the Novocure lung cancer trial."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"You can see, in her case,"},{"time":796000,"text":"she's wearing her transducer arrays,"},{"time":798000,"text":"one of the front of her chest, one on the back,"},{"time":801000,"text":"and then the second pair side-to-side over the liver."},{"time":804000,"text":"You can see the Tumor Treating Field field generator,"},{"time":807000,"text":"but importantly you can also see that she is living her life."},{"time":810000,"text":"She is managing her farm."},{"time":812000,"text":"She's interacting with her kids and her grand kids."},{"time":815000,"text":"And when we talked to her,"},{"time":818000,"text":"she said that when she was undergoing chemotherapy,"},{"time":820000,"text":"she had to go to the hospital every month for her infusions."},{"time":823000,"text":"Her whole family suffered"},{"time":825000,"text":"as her side effect profile came and went."},{"time":827000,"text":"Now she can run"},{"time":829000,"text":"all of the activities of her farm."},{"time":832000,"text":"It's only the beginning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":834000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":841000,"text":"In the lab, we've observed tremendous synergies"},{"time":845000,"text":"between chemotherapy and Tumor Treating Fields."},{"time":848000,"text":"There's research underway now at Harvard Medical School"},{"time":851000,"text":"to pick the optimum pairs"},{"time":853000,"text":"to maximize that benefit."},{"time":855000,"text":"We also believe that Tumor Treating Fields will work with radiation"},{"time":858000,"text":"and interrupt the self-repair mechanisms that we have."},{"time":862000,"text":"There's now a new research project underway"},{"time":864000,"text":"at the Karolinska in Sweden"},{"time":866000,"text":"to prove that hypothesis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":868000,"text":"We have more trials planned"},{"time":870000,"text":"for lung cancer,"},{"time":872000,"text":"pancreatic cancer, ovarian cancer"},{"time":874000,"text":"and breast cancer."},{"time":876000,"text":"And I firmly believe"},{"time":878000,"text":"that in the next 10 years"},{"time":880000,"text":"Tumor Treating Fields"},{"time":882000,"text":"will be a weapon available to doctors and patients"},{"time":885000,"text":"for all of these most-difficult-to-treat solid tumors."},{"time":891000,"text":"I'm also very hopeful"},{"time":893000,"text":"that in the next decades,"},{"time":895000,"text":"we will make big strides"},{"time":897000,"text":"on reducing that death rate"},{"time":900000,"text":"that has been so challenging in this disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":903000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":905000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}